abstract: Bay County, Fla, police arrest 22-year-old David Jamichael Daniels of Mobile, Ala, and charge him with shooting seven young men and women at town house in Panama City Beach during spring break; no fatalities are reported; Daniels is charged with seven counts of attempted murder.
lead_paragraph: Several Alabama A&M students were among the victims Saturday in Panama City Beach, Fla. An Alabama man was arrested.

headline.main: 7 Wounded in Spring Break Shooting in Florida
